= Creation of a new release =

To create a new release of yume, please do the following:
- Check and update if necessary the ChangeLog if needed (at least remove the "not yet released")
- Check and Update the version in the Makefile if needed
- Check and Update the version in the spec file if needed
- Set the spec file release tag to a number >= 1
- Check and Update Update the version in the Debian changelog.

After the release:
- Update the version in the ChangeLog (with the "not yet released comment")
- Update the version in the Makefile
- Update the version in the spec file
- Set the spec file release to 0.1
- Update the version in the debian/changelog

